{"tid":2174322,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"老蕭 : 泛民應立即全力爭取恢復選舉, 一旦接受留任就是放棄恢復選舉, 及民調搬龍門","createTime":"2020-08-25T23:31:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-25T23:53:48.000Z","uid":279631,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e588b21b4febfa9c807d531d0cfafd80b6e0b4b4","tid":2174322,"uid":279631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T23:31:09.000Z","msg":"BurnHill:<br />\n「而家跌到十個八個確診, 就應該選舉, 怎麼還不爭取選舉? <span class=\"blue\">一旦接受了選舉, 就即係唔使選舉啦? </span>而家五眼聯盟迫緊北京恢復選舉, 接受委任, 就冇得選舉, <span class=\"blue\">兩樣野係唔可以同時存在</span>...」<br />\n「民主黨/鍾劍華搞的民調, 搬龍門搬到咁, 不如唔好搞民調, 唔好<strong><span class=\"red\">扮</span></strong>係跟民調...」<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">(民主黨/鍾劍華搞的民調要雙門檻，即整體受訪者過半數有決定，或民主派支持者中超過三分之二有同一傾向，民主黨才跟從結果。)</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/gYPWMY9ofNk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FgYPWMY9ofNk&d=mfTbPTXtdXcWugdQC%2B6BDqEbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=1f7eb82b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/gYPWMY9ofNk</a><br />\n(由12:30開始)"},{"pid":"8d1b620ed7df1237e67dc7b82e2ca6c6a8b23aac","tid":2174322,"uid":120480,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T23:53:48.000Z","msg":"其實同渣哥無分别，真係撐唔到"}]}